  "title": "🎤 Karaoke Assistant | Islandwide | Day or Night | Gross Up to $3,000 + Bonus + Perks",
  "description": "<h3>🕒 Working Hours:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Full-Time | 6 Days Work Week</strong></li>\n  <li>Day or Night Shift</li>\n  <li>Off days arranged by schedule</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>🎯 Key Responsibilities:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide friendly and courteous service to guests.</li>\n  <li>Handle phone calls for reservations and general inquiries.</li>\n  <li>Greet and direct guests to their reserved tables.</li>\n  <li>Take and record food &amp; beverage orders promptly.</li>\n  <li>Input orders into POS system accurately.</li>\n  <li>Serve food &amp; drinks efficiently while maintaining high quality standards.</li>\n  <li>Ensure safe, clean, and organized service areas.</li>\n  <li>Communicate effectively with team members and supervisors.</li>\n  <li>Uphold neat and professional appearance at all times.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable handling alcoholic beverages in a nightlife setting.</li>\n  <li>Perform ad-hoc duties as required.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>✅ Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prior F&amp;B or service crew experience preferred.</li>\n  <li>Strong communication &amp; interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Ability to multitask in a fast-paced nightlife environment.</li>\n  <li>Positive attitude, team spirit, and strong work ethic.</li>\n  <li>Comfortable with night shifts &amp; serving alcoholic drinks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Perks You’ll Enjoy:</strong><br>\n✔️ Medical &amp; Dental Benefits<br>\n✔️ Birthday Ang Pao 🎂<br>\n✔️ Company Transport 🚌<br>\n✔️ Incremental Annual Leave (starting from 10 days)<br>\n✔️ Career Advancement Opportunities</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Nicholas Wong</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R23113643</p>\n<p>EA License No: 23C1703</p>",
